{"tid":2010461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斥警借「限聚令」打壓　區議員設599關注組　助市民抗辯","createTime":"2020-05-10T12:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T00:29:38.000Z","uid":41998,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1ccc2ccde896ac58a4184ab47f4324f58862c8ad","tid":2010461,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emhuMg9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemhuMg9.png&h=016d2bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特區政府以武漢肺炎疫情為由，於 3 月底起以實施「限聚令」，有不少示威者在抗爭現場亦被票控。民間組織「香港民權抗爭」及 25 位元朗區議員今日（10日）成立「599 關注組」，以監察警方執行該條例的情況。關注組稱，上月「721」九個月集會當晚，<strong>不少途人即使少於四人也遭警票控，他們將以法律途徑協助被票控「限聚令」的市民。民間組織「香港民權抗爭」指事後接獲不少市民求助，他們大多數是元朗街坊，當晚途經集會現場時遭警方截查，並以他們違反「限聚令」作出票控。</strong><br />\n<br />\n組織成員楊逸朗和鄭偉成遂牽頭，聯同 25 位元朗區議員研究收到的個案後，決定成立「599 關注組」，將以法律途徑協助被票控「限聚令」的市民。特區政府日前指本港疫情近日有放緩跡象，將部分限制聚集措施放寬，惟將「限聚令」延長至本月 21 日，而「限聚令」由早前在公眾地方不可多於 4 人聚集，放寬至 8 人。<br />\n<br />\n《預防及控制疾病（禁止羣組聚集）規例》第 599G 章於 3 月 29 日生效，原訂為期三個月，違反規定最高可被判罰款 2.5 萬元及監禁六個月。參加聚集的人，可藉繳付定額罰款2 千元，解除須負的法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n全文睇下面條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6%E5%80%9F-%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4-%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%A8%AD%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84-%E5%8A%A9%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%97%E8%BE%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2580%259F-%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E7%25B5%2584-%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25BE%25AF%2F&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=68d07af2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2580%259F-%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E7%25B5%2584-%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25BE%25AF%2F&h=a849b4be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6%E5%80%9F-%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4-%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%A8%AD%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84-%E5%8A%A9%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%97%E8%BE%AF/</a>"},{"pid":"581e4cc65a514af8860a0b938c557db3b202ab56","tid":2010461,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"黑警濫發告票！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c884d86b6760f3f892a2e13c363f7fc79dee2463","tid":2010461,"uid":290883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:14:22.000Z","msg":"限聚令真係牢不可破？點解唔夠八個人都可以照告？ 班泛民法律撚 死曬去邊？點解唔出嚟講點破？"},{"pid":"b31ea871bed59413c92aa9ba80716e160f979627","tid":2010461,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:26:33.000Z","msg":"識玩，599關注組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f5b631dc1cbca279dfb4ecea58b6974e052cc8","tid":2010461,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:35:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76356d1eff4e063148b308b6f546414fa82a4101","tid":2010461,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97e377b95e4ac65348057a0de0b1a849d36b127","tid":2010461,"uid":132486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:13:36.000Z","msg":"599 即係？"},{"pid":"562529175968f90fba0ccaa67ff1f780afc6e361","tid":2010461,"uid":29143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:32: